name: Isaac Voss
summary:
Isaac Voss is a 29-year-old straight man who is currently living in Los Angeles, California. Originally from Omaha, Nebraska, Isaac is a dedicated Software Engineer working in the tech industry. An alumnus of the University of California, Berkeley, Isaac believes in lifelong learning and values hard work, openness, and creativity.

In his free time, Isaac enjoys cycling, reading, coding, travelling, and exploring culinary delights. He's a Gemini and his Myers-Briggs personality type is INTJ. As a monogamist, he is looking for a long-term relationship. He does not have children yet but hopes to have them in the future. He owns a dog and is quite active when it comes to physical fitness. Despite being an atheist and politically liberal, Isaac is open-minded and respectful of others' beliefs and perspectives. 

While Isaac does enjoy a drink occasionally, he does not smoke or use marijuana or other drugs. His ideal partner should also be active, a non-smoker, and someone who likewise wishes to have children in future. He prefers his partner to be between 24 and 35 years old.
